900503-0148.
</DOCID>
<HL>
   Who's News:
   M.A. Hanna Co.
</HL>
<DATE>
05/03/90
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE B8
</SO>
<CO>
   WNEWS MAH
</CO>
<LP>
   M.A. HANNA Co. (Cleveland) -- Douglas J. McGregor, Hanna's
president and chief operating officer; Jack L. Cockwell,
executive vice president and chief operating officer of
Brascan Ltd.; and Paul M. Marshall, Brascan's vice chairman,
were elected directors of this plastics and other polymers
company. Four directors retired, reducing the board to 12
members.
</LP>
