days (priced at par). 10.61%, standard conventional
fixed-rate mortgages; 9.25%, 6/2 rate capped one-year
adjustable rate mortgages. Source: Telerate Systems Inc.
                                                                                                       

   MERRILL LYNCH READY ASSETS TRUST: 7.66%. Annualized
average rate of return after expenses for the past 30 days;
not a forecast of future returns.
